  m_Name: Bow_1
  m_EditorClassIdentifier: 
  itemName: Moonreaper
  itemDescription: "The limbs of this bow were carved from the ribs of the creature
    that hunted by moonlight for three centuries. Its string is woven from sinew
    that still contracts with the phases of the moon \u2014 loosest at new moon,
    tightest at full. Arrows fired from it arc in a crescent path, curving toward
    warmth. They have never once missed a beating heart."
  itemImage: {fileID: 1819778140, guid: 7698f902a8e73cb4b88c4738f7fb0ff5, type: 3}
