  <PassiveName>k__BackingField: Piercing shot
  <PassiveDesc>k__BackingField: "<color=#FFD700>Hold attack</color> to draw fully.
    <color=#FF5555>Released arrow</color> <color=#FFA500>pierces through all enemies</color>
    in its path and deals <color=#42EADDFF><b>\xD71.8 damage</b></color> to each."
